PrecisRegulations Amending the COMPREHENSIVE STUDY LIST REGULATIONS by adding the terms "hazardous waste" and "marine terminal" to the Interpretation section and defining their meaning, and by clarifying how other sections of the Regulations are to be applied to designated projects or classes of projects for which a comprehensive study is required.

precis:
Regulations Amending the COMPREHENSIVE STUDY LIST REGULATIONS by adding the
terms "hazardous waste" and "marine terminal" to the Interpretation section
and defining their meaning, and by clarifying how other sections of the
Regulations are to be applied to designated projects or classes of projects
for which a comprehensive study is required.
